SOPHIE'S CURSE! ►► https://goo.gl/ejAOm2
FNAF: Sister Location Custom Nights! ►► https://goo.gl/lALgny

Remember Ferbies? I recall the feeling of joy when I got mine. Then I discovered how terrifying they are once the lights are out. TATTLETAIL is the game that reaffirms exactly how scary those furry fellas really are. If you can handle the horror, join us for a frightfully Ferby-fearing episode of GT Live!

Subscribe & hang out with us every day! ►► http://bit.ly/1Oo7KH9
Follow us on Twitter at @MatPatGT and #GTLive

More GTLive Videos:
Sister Location (Official Release) ►►http://bit.ly/2e5xeOT

Don't YIFF FOXY! Dayshift at Freddy's ►► http://bit.ly/GTLyiff
Weirdest Quiz Ever | Guess the Wikihow ► http://bit.ly/2gh4IpQ
TORTURED by One Night At FLUMPTY'S!►► http://bit.ly/20VUcEs
Sad Puppet is Sad! - FNAC Part 1 ►► http://bit.ly/1U8Xs0I

Don't have much time but need a quick fix? Check out some of our highlight episodes for hilarious moments from our live streams. Here are a few to get you started.

HiLite: FNAF Theorists Surprised By Scott! ► http://bit.ly/1Jrlm3i
